title: NEW! NuFACE Curated Collections with Expert Beauty Insiders
description:
Introducing the limited edition NuFACE Curated Collections! We've partnered with celebrity aesthetician Shani Darden and lifestyle and beauty blogger Lisa Allen to bring you their hand-selected beauty must-haves for the holiday. 

Learn more about why these expert beauty insiders can't stop talking about microcurrent facial-lifts and check out their curated collections. 
Check out the Haute Contour and Glam On-The-Go Curated Collections from NuFACE: http://bit.ly/YTHoliday2016
